♪ There's a feeling I get

1:19:24.967 --> 1:19:27.467
♪ When I think of Christmas

1:19:27.600 --> 1:19:31.433
♪ Just a glimmer of hope

1:19:31.567 --> 1:19:33.467
♪ That I long to witness

1:19:33.600 --> 1:19:36.600
♪ Like a star above

